getFirstHDUAttributes

public void getFirstHDUAttributes()
As we know, all the spectrum have identical attributeHandle. These attribute came from the first HDU, so this method gets all the comon attribute from the first HDU.

getParametersData

public void getParametersData()

createAllMapAttributes

public void createAllMapAttributes()
This method creates all the mapAttributes for each spectrum. It takes the attributes from the first HDU, and add to it the attributes of each spectrum (parameters name and new combination of values).
